               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Sǝnkǝssar "Synaxarion" for three months of the year (fols.
                     3ra-146rb)
 I-1) Tāḫśāś (fols. 3ra–51rc)
 I-2) Ṭǝrr (fols.
                     51va-104va)
 I-3) Yakkātit (fols. 105ra-146rb)
 The commemorative
                     notices are followed by ʿarke-hymns
 
 Additiones 1-3.</summary>
