                  <additions>
                     <list>
                        <item xml:id="a1"> <locus target="#146rb">f. 146rb</locus>
                           <desc>l.17: Purchase note.</desc>
                           <quote xml:lang="gez"> <locus target="#146rb">146rb</locus> l.17: ዛቲ፡
                              መጽሐፍ፡ ዘአቡነ፡ ሊባኖስ፡ መስጥህ፡ ዳኛው፡ በላታ፡ ተሰማ፡ እማኞች፡ ሀለቃ፡ ማሩ፡ መምሬ፡ ተክሉ፡ ሀለቃ፡
                              ወልደ፡ ንጉሥ፡ አቶ፡ ደረስ፡ ኢራር፡ እለቱ፡ ሰኞ፡ ወርኁ፡ ጥር፡ ዘመኑ፡ ዮሐንስ፡ ሻጩ፡ መምሬ፡ ገብረ፡
                              ማርያም፡</quote>
                           <quote xml:lang="en">
                              <locus target="#146rb">146rb</locus> l.17: This is the book of (the
                              church of) ʾabuna Libānos Mäsṭǝh, the judge (is) bälatta Täsämma, the
                              witnesses are haläqa Maru, mämǝre Täklu, haläqa Walda Nǝguś, ʾato
                              Därräs ʾIrar, (in) the day of Monday, the month of Ṭǝrr (in the) year
                              of John, the seller is Gabra Māryām. </quote> In Amharic. The note is
                           probably written in the same hand as the one that added later the donor´s
                           name. The church of ʾabuna<note> Libānos Mäsṭǝh is also mentioned in
                              Additiones 1, 3 in MR-037. </note>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a2"> <locus target="#146rc">f. 146rc</locus>
                           <desc>l.1: Supplication note (?)</desc>
                           <quote xml:lang="gez">
                              <locus target="#146rc">146rc</locus> l.1: ንህነ፡ ወኢትዝከር፡ ኵሉ፡ አበሳነ፡ አበሳ፡
                              ኃጢአት፡ </quote>
                           <quote xml:lang="en"/>
                           <note> </note>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a3">
                           <locus target="#141rc">f. 141rc</locus>
                           <desc>: Za-ʾaqrabku māḥleta… “The song I am offering…” (concluding
                              prayer).</desc>
                           <quote xml:lang="gez">
                              <locus target="#141rc">141rc</locus>: ዘአቅረብኩ፡ ማህሌተ፡ አዘኪርየ፡ አዕላፈ፡ እምእለ፡
                              ተፀምዱከ፡ ዘልፈ፡ ለለአነብብ፡ ተወከፍ፡ ዘንዴትየ፡ መጽሃፈ፡ ...</quote>
                           <quote xml:lang="en"/>
                           <note> </note>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="e1">- The title of the text is crudely written on <locus target="#1r">1r</locus>, in pencil.
 - Pen trials on <locus target="#2r">2r</locus> (black ink), 146v (written in black, deep
                           reddish brown, very deep purple ink and pencil).
 - Several
                           corrections written interlineally in blue pen (e.g., <locus target="#3va">3va</locus> l.4, 11rb l.4, 11rc l.12).</item>
                     </list>
